#

Miso-Glazed Black Cod

30 min
$20
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

Japanese

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

QuickHealthyAsian InspiredFish

Description

A rich and buttery black cod fillet glazed with sweet miso, perfect for a quick yet elegant dinner.

Ingredients

  • black cod fillets: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • miso paste: 3 tablespoons
  • brown sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • soy sauce: 1 tablespoon
  • sake (or white wine): 1 tablespoon
  • sesame oil: 1 teaspoon
  • green onions: for garnish (optional)
